==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blizzard
<hw>Bliz"zard</hw> <pr>(bl⟦icr⟧z"z⟦etil⟧rd)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. <er>Blaze</er> to flash. Formerly, in local use, a rattling
volley; cf. ⟦ldquo⟧to <ets>blaze</ets> away⟦rdquo⟧ to fire away.]</ety>
<def>A gale of piercingly cold wind, usually accompanied with fine and
blinding snow; a furious blast.</def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

